guide: Â§7Use the best fishing rod, bait and armor that you
Â§7have access to and fish in The Park during rain.
Â§7Recommended is a Chum Rod with Angler Armor and Fish Bait.
Â§7This requires Raw Fish Collection 5.
Â§7You should place down fishing minions
Â§7with medium storages and fuel to help with this.
Â§7To help with this, try to make bigger crafts
Â§7by hand for Carpentry levels.
Â§7Use the gold from the Collection goal
Â§7to brew Absorption potions.
Â§7Also do your daily experiments and make sure
Â§7to have a pet active at all times
Â§7(any pet works, even level 100).
Â§7Optimally you want to use a weapon with
Â§7Luck 5+ and Looting 3+ and aim for
Â§7good magic find. Grab the Century Cakes for
Â§7+1 Magic Find for 2 days.
Â§7Optimal tool:
Â§7Golden Axe with Efficiency 5
Â§7Reforges: Lumberjack's or Moil
Â§7Get Haste 3 from a splash to instamine wood
Â§7You might want to grab the Bee Mask from Carnival
Â§7while its still active.
Â§7Use the best pickaxe you have access to
Â§7and enchant it. Then mine Gold in the
Â§7Dwarven Mines. The Ability Pickobolus unlocked
Â§7at Heart of the Mountain 3 might be a decent help.
Â§7You will need Combat 12 for this.
Â§7Getting a Void Sword and Ender Armor
Â§7will make progress in this easier.
Â§7Wear a full set of Ender equipment. Those drop from:
Â§7Endermen (0.5% chance), Ender Nodes (3.05% - 3.32% chance),
Â§7Obsidian Defenders (1% chance) and Watchers (1% chance).
Â§7You can find these Mobs in the Dragon's Nest in the End.
Â§7Brew an Absorption IV potion
Â§7with the Enchanted Gold from the Collector Goal
Â§7and combine it with a Glowstone.
Â§7You can get that Glowstone by buying one block
Â§7from the Builder and breaking it on your island.
Â§7Craft some easy minions while also getting
Â§7those that will help with this Bingo.
Â§7Use NPC shops to buy materials for easy crafts.
Â§7Kill farm animals in the Barn with a Cleaver
Â§7with Cleave 5 and Sharpness 5
Â§7or spiders in Arachne's Burrow
Â§7in the Spider's Den with a Dreadlord Sword.
Â§7You can also kill Endermen in The End to
Â§7get progress towards the
Â§7Enderman Slayer Community Goal.
Â§7This unlocks at 5k Diamond Collection. Use Pure Ores
Â§7in the Dwarven Mines for this. Craft it with
Â§71 Enchanted Diamond and 8 Vines (costs 40 Jungle Leaves,
Â§7requires Jungle Wood Collection 4 to unlock it in /trades.)
Â§7Do your daily experiments in the Experimentation Table,
Â§7always do the highest tier you can.
Â§7You will most likely get this passively.
Â§7Use /be ingame to view your progress once you
Â§7talked to Bramass Beastslayer in The Spiders Den.
Â§7Collect those you run along while doing other goals.
Â§7If you have trouble check TimeDeo's fairy soul tutorial
Â§7on YouTube or use /neusouls on.
Â§7You'll unlock this recipe passively
Â§7(250 leather collection)
Â§7if you chose to do Exterminator in Barn.
Â§7Craft it with 80 Leather.
Â§7You can also use Cow Minions for this.

30.description: Â§7Obtain a Campfire Cultist Badge I
guide: Â§7Visit the Campfire in The Park and do
Â§7the first Trial of Fire. (10 dps over 10s)
Â§7Farm Mushroom Blocks in the Desert
Â§7with an Efficiency 5 Silk Touch 1 Gold Axe.
Â§7Obtain the needed Glowstone by buying a
Â§7Glowstone Block from the Builder and breaking
Â§7it on your island.

32.description: Â§7Gain coins from the Scavenger Enchantment
guide: Â§7Kill mobs with a weapon that you have
Â§7Scavenger 3+ applied to.
Â§7You will most likely get this from
Â§7leveling up skills.
Â§7Remember to actually put the money
Â§7you get in the Bank :)
Â§7Reforge your Void Sword to Sharp
Â§7at the Blacksmith in the Hub or
Â§7enchant any weapon with Critical 5 (50 Levels).
Â§7Optimal tool:
Â§7Advanced Gardening Hoe (25 copper)
Â§7Make a full plot of Wheat (7896 seeds needed)
Â§7in The Garden (SkyBlock Level 5)
Â§7Get the seeds to plant from The Barn
Â§7or from the farm area in The Hub.
Â§7Get yourself a splash, equip a Bingo Pet
Â§7and get the cake buff by eating the cakes
Â§7on nightlibra's, skyerzz's or prtl's island.
Â§7If this doesn't finish it, get a Void Sword (200k) in the End
Â§7and hold it while some Ender Armor and/or Equipment.
Â§7Use the best fishing rod, bait and armor that you
Â§7have access to and fish in The Park during rain.
Â§7Recommended is a Chum Rod with Angler Armor and Fish Bait.
Â§7Make sure to have Looting 3+ applied to your
Â§7weapon and rod.
Â§7You can lootshare bigger mobs like Nutcrackers on
Â§7the Winter Island for this too.
Â§7Â§cAsk before you randomly hit peoples mobs.
Â§7Mine normal or Pure Ores in the Dwarven Mines.
Â§7You will gain passive progress in this if you
Â§7manual the Gold Collector Goal.
